node.text: Here are your standings for Conquer the Rock. Congratulations to all the drivers that participated. Check your messages as prizes will be gifted soon!

Check out these shots from @jspxrr featuring our 2020 Special Olympics livery. Here's what @jspxrr has to share with the photo community: "Make sure your photos look good for yourself first, others can wait. If you really like somebody's photo and wish you could make that, practice making similar to it, because it's progression too! Don't be afraid if your photos look like copying, it can be a hard work to get to a point of someone's level. Inspiration is everything!"

node.text: Advice from @txzm_virtualphoto: “As I work in advertisement and show industry, when doing a screenshot I often ask myself is a screenshot looks good enough to be printed in a motorsport magazine. Do my works always look good enough? Definitely not! However Forza games give enormous freedom of experimenting with a vast variety of light- and weather conditions to be sure that you can find your perfect shot!”
